 expand on this empirical illustration and\nintroduce a new metric p---the Activity Momentum---to assess the activity\nrobustness of collaboration networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 May 2015 09:18:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Feb 2016 13:32:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-02"}
